name: SRPhoneUsageReport
desc: An object that describes the user’s phone activity over a period of time.

items.name: var duration: TimeInterval
items.desc: The duration that the report spans.

items.name: var totalIncomingCalls: Int
items.desc: The number of calls the user receives.

items.name: var totalOutgoingCalls: Int
items.desc: The number of calls the user makes.

items.name: var totalPhoneCallDuration: TimeInterval
items.desc: The total duration of all calls.
